name: Terra Nova Blue Lagoon Full Cast
description:
50% of proceeds will be donated to the wereachfoundation.org for Haiti's earthquake victims.

This photo is from the short film "Lifestyle of a new age low key Investor" The members of this cast are comprised of gold, crypto, and real estate investors. Our cast was strategically assembled to showcase some of Miami's local businesses and professionals. Also local business owners make cameo appearances and product placements. The Blue Lagoon Redland Farm in Homestead, Florida, location was used in the film storyline, as an off-grid private meet up, where new age low key investors network. All of our talent has been combined to bring awareness and raise funds for Haiti's earthquake victims.

Executive producer and music produced by 
J. Classic-Maestro

Creative Director Maicol Diaz
